# Getting Started

Clone the repository:
git clone git@github.com:crahen/vision.git

Create a workspace outside the repository:
mkdir build

Configure and build:
cd build
../vision/configure && make

# Cross-Compiling

For Raspberry PI:

SYSROOT=<extracted sysroot image>
configure --host=arm-linux-gnueabihf --with-sysroot=$SYSROOT --prefix=/tmp/test
